*Ja* volim da pevam. (I love to sing.)
*On* me je pitao da li *ja* želim da idem sa njim. (He asked me if I wanted to go with him.)
*Mi* smo se družili, a *ja* sam bio najsrećniji. (We were hanging out and I was the happiest.)
*Ti* si me pitao da li *ja* znam odgovor. (You asked me if I knew the answer.)
*Vi* ste me pitali da li *ja* znam šta ću uraditi. (You asked me if I knew what to do.)